sources.title: George A. Romero Presents Deadtime Stories Vol. 1 - Full Movie
sources.description:
An anthology of 3 terrifying horror stories presented by horror mastermind George A. Romero. Young lovers are attacked by a mysterious creature, a lonely man opens a mysterious box and a woman searches for her missing husband in the jungles of South America.
